      <h2>How to Grow Your Business Online in 2025 — Simple Steps</h2>
      <p>In 2025, having a strong online presence is no longer optional — it’s essential. Whether you’re a small business or a growing brand, your website is your digital storefront.</p>
      <h3>1. Build a Modern Website</h3>
      <p>Your website should be fast, mobile-friendly, and visually appealing. Use clear messages and calls to action that guide visitors to your services.</p>

      <h3>2. Optimize for SEO</h3>
      <p>Search engine optimization helps your business get discovered. Focus on keywords related to your products and services.</p>

      <h3>3. Use Social Media</h3>
      <p>Share valuable content on social media platforms to connect with potential customers and build trust in your brand.</p>

      <h3>4. Invest in Digital Advertising</h3>
      <p>Platforms like Google Ads and Meta Ads help you reach targeted audiences and bring real traffic to your website.</p>
